title: Does a Photo Show Trump’s Children with Lev Parnas and Igor Fruman?
subtitle: Real photographs do exist of Donald Trump with the men arrested on suspicion of scheming to funnel foreign money into his campaign.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A photograph shows the adult children of U.S. President Donald Trump — Ivanka, Eric, and Donald Trump Jr. — with Lev Parnas and Igor Fruman.
